Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:16.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared all I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:18.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I just have to do it \Nthe way I practiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:23.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever want to feel like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:30.09,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Finish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:32.91,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Boom! Whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:35.05,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Rat-tat-tat-tat, kaboom!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:39.56,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, I'm guessing you're \Nfeeling a little better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.12,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-Blammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.92,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Crack! Boosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:45.56,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:47.62,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nanamin! What can I do for ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:50.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I was wondering how your \Nwork was coming along...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:53.32,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's just pounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:55.45,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't love wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:56.45,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:59.28,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the script Jin wrote!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:04.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was an action story...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:05.36,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.48,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:13.94,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nanamin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:16.72,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, could I borrow this script?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.04,0:01:17.66,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:20.77,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be grateful if you let me \Nuse this for my audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:21.69,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:23.10,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,February 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:25.29,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:26.58,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:31.65,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Out of three scripts, I'm allowed to \Nperform one I've chosen myself, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.78,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'd love you to perform it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:36.56,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Use it however you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:38.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:41.22,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an ally of all hardworking girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:43.51,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's time for me to work hard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:48.84,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Boom! B-B-Blam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:50.47,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh, whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:54.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,February 14th...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:30.60,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1)}#16 I've Always Loved You
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.35,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming Call
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.35,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda Yuko
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:33.77,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so energetic \Nthis early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:38.11,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's you who's not energetic {\i1}enough{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.18,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,The Suimei exam is on February \N13th, so I'll be staying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:42.28,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with you the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.97,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You agreed! You don't usually \Naccept things {\i1}this{\i0} easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:49.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You'd show up even if I told you not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:49.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hanging up—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:53.31,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cold! You're as cold as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Today's an important day for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm presenting my pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:57.71,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,A pitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:58.91,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Does it taste good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:00.95,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:01.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take that seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:04.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a test, sorta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:06.66,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,So you've got a test too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.39,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll share some of my energy with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.18,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:11.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:23.07,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, you look pale. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:23.99,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Your presentation's today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:27.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah, after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:28.56,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:29.99,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks. I'll give it my best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:37.55,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:40.27,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting so fired \Nup on a cold day like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:45.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How was Australia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.82,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that, Kanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:50.23,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't even started yet, \Nand you're stiff as a board, honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:52.02,Sign,MUG,0000,0000,0000,,Love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:52.02,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about being perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:55.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? But I need to do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.52,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.48,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you to not try so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:05.28,Saku-main,PRINCIPAL,0000,0000,0000,,The new year has begun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:08.71,Saku-main,STUDENT A,0000,0000,0000,,The principal goes on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.36,Saku-main,STUDENT B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.41,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, kouhai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Jin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:27.17,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:28.16,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:37.19,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,No one can top my bullfrog impression!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sound so smug about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:43.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Senpai. You want to \Ntalk to Jin-san, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.07,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:47.45,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:51.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san, aren't you coming \Nback to Sakura Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.28,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I'll be staying at...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:57.08,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the former Student Council President's \Nplace until after the exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.62,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, nobody told me this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.05,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:01.51,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't agree to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:02.59,Saku-main,HIMEMIYA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.64,Saku-main,HIMEMIYA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Soichiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:10.76,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hau-Hau, I see you've only\N got eyes for Soichiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:14.15,Saku-main,HIMEMIYA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. He's my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:15.77,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,How innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:20.48,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could have experienced \Na love like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:22.31,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:23.55,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:24.65,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.77,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to hog \Nthe precious little time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:29.10,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,a couple gets together before graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:31.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:34.16,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's the situation. \NLet Misaki know for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.10,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:42.00,Saku-main,SOICHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,If you're done here, do you mind\Ntaking that bullfrog with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:48.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised the former \NStudent Council President...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.01,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,knew that was a bullfrog you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:54.31,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:54.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:56.35,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I want to move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.99,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,So you've got to give it your best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:07.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:15.81,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is face them with all \Nmy energy, anxiety, and insecurity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:25.25,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama Nanami
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:25.25,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,To: Kanda-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.79,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I know this might only put pressure on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.51,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,but I still want to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:32.84,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.85,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:39.77,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Send
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:38.64,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,At least I can text her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:45.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kanda Sorata. Thank you for your...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:52.88,Saku-main,PRESIDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Fujisawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.82,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.32,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anyone actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:58.04,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,hit their head on the mic before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:00.87,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I just witnessed a rare sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:06.46,Saku-thought,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you to not try so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:17.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to explain my "Rhythm \NBattler" pitch to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:21.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rhythm action battle game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:21.31,Sign,SLIDE,0000,0000,0000,,Rhythm Battler
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:21.31,Sign,SLIDE,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Genre:{\b0} Rhythm Action Battle Game
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:26.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Players attack by pushing buttons \Nin time with the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:32.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The goal is to defeat the enemy \Ncharacter before the song ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:35.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Moving on, I'll explain \Nwhat the controls are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:39.74,Sign,SLIDE,0000,0000,0000,,Attack by pushing the buttons in time with the music!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:39.74,Sign,SLIDE,0000,0000,0000,,Perform combos to achieve high scores!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:40.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The combined effect of video and \Nmusic makes this project unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:44.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Once the player has completed \Na song, he can play back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:47.46,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the video and upload it \Nas a stylish music video.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:50.58,Saku-main,PRESIDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Fujisawa, if you were to make this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:52.51,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Recently, it has become \Npossible to download music...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.05,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,how much would it cost to develop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:57.20,Saku-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}and video using smartphones \Nand mobile devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.43,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Including debugging costs, \Nprobably around 100 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.34,Saku-main,PRESIDENT,0000,0000,0000,,What if you outsource it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:02.22,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Individuals can also easily upload...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.49,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Probably 10 million for a prototype...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.10,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and 70 million to finish it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.81,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,People would probably make faces no \Nmatter where we tried to market it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:05.51,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}their own videos to express themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:08.26,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but at 2,200 yen a unit, \Nwe'd break even at...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:08.79,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Particularly good videos actually receive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:12.21,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}a greater number of views and \Nthus garner more attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:10.68,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,around 45,000 units.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:13.15,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that would make our \Nsales target 100,000 units.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:15.86,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}In other words, I believe these videos \Nwill do much to promote the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.03,Saku-main,PRESIDENT,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:22.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I would like to \Nsummarize my concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:26.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Stylishly defeating your enemies in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:29.12,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with the music is the core of this project.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:31.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to create a game that \Nexhilarates the player...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:34.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and allows them to share \Nthat feeling on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:38.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A game that is both fun \Nto play and fun to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes my pitch presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:48.64,Saku-main,PRESIDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kanda Sorata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:52.46,Saku-main,PRESIDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, we've concluded \Nthat it'd be difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.57,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,for our company to release your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:03.54,Saku-main,PRESIDENT,0000,0000,0000,,However, would you be \Nwilling to let our staff...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.79,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,help you polish your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:09.53,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you've partially passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:14.34,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,When you get home, send us an email.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.42,Sign,CARD,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Game Director{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.42,Sign,CARD,0000,0000,0000,,Fujisawa Kazuki
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:17.00,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're ready for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:19.18,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll decide on a date \Nfor our next meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:23.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.23,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,The presentation was a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.23,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.23,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:42.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.47,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:51.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I know there's no point in \Nasking, but I will anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:53.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we having red \Nrice and motsunabe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.98,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're celebrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.86,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The motsunabe shows respect to Hakata!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:57.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Encore, Hakata!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was pointless asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.39,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll serve up some for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:07.06,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,It's like eating okonomiyaki \Nwith a spatula.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.56,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:15.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're celebrating with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:19.07,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but it takes time for a pitch \Nto actually go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't actually succeeded yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:24.87,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll have to plan a bigger \Ncelebration when you actually pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:29.50,Saku-main,RYUNOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Most people don't even make it \Nto the presentation stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:30.84,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:33.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me. \NThanks for the text, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:35.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I hope it didn't bug you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It really motivated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:38.48,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:39.39,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Text?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:43.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just before my \Npresentation, Aoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:45.38,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,sent me a text telling me I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:49.50,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:57.32,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.99,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.99,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,No Subject
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.99,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, what kind of joke is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.71,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You said texts motivate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to text me now, \Nyou should be saying "Congratulations."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.31,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Your reaction was different \Nfor Nanami's text.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:16.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:17.79,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is this discrimination?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:18.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:20.80,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You only give Nanami special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten that I give you \Nspecial treatment every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:28.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, thanks for the pitch \Nillustration, Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:31.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It made it a lot easier \Nto explain my concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.07,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:33.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:37.48,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.23,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:41.93,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn next, Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.24,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:50.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with your audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:52.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:54.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:58.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's a favor \NI want to ask of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.34,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Would that be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:10.93,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually pretty important, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:18.81,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's actually something I've \Nalways wanted to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:21.44,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.40,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:26.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Always...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.51,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've always loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:31.04,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:46.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I also l-l-lo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Don't be so \Nembarrassed about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.60,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're making me embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.37,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,We're just acting, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:02.04,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's take it from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:02.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:06.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:09.99,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually pretty important, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:16.08,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Watching Kanda-kun and Aoyama-san \Ntogether makes you feel gloomy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:20.38,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by gloomy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.25,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I get this weird feeling right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:25.46,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:30.93,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:33.32,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important time for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.89,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Read these and study them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.52,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,And pour all that gloom into your manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.69,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Pour it into my manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:48.11,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Nanami, this is your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu, you say that every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:54.45,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,But it says, "I love you" \Nin the script, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:57.47,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you use it as an excuse \Nto confess your feelings to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:58.70,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:02.03,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kanda agreed to help you, \Nit means he's not against the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.96,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine's Day is coming \Nup, so it'd be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:06.67,Saku-main,NAMAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.42,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for my audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:11.22,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go into that with impure motives!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.14,Saku-main,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,You're always so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.94,Saku-main,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.82,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,February 14th is Valentine's Day
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:35.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:39.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually pretty important, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's actually something I've \Nalways wanted to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:45.25,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:45.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Always...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.01,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Always...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:54.51,Saku-thought,MAYU,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you use it as an excuse \Nto confess your feelings to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.59,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't, I can't, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:14.93,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.95,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're working hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:30.49,Sign,MANGA,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:32.12,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.34,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine's Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.95,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move forward with \Nthis game concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:44.52,Sign,BOARD,0000,0000,0000,,Rhythm Battler
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:44.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:47.40,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, that illustration \Nfrom your presentation...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:50.15,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Who drew that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:52.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's Sakura Hall's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:56.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, someone living \Nin my dorm drew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.65,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.71,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of Chihiro-sensei's \Nstudents, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:04.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You know Chihiro-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:06.79,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we were classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:11.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Her cousin drew that illustration!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:12.82,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.52,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Did she also work on Nyapollon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:17.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she helped with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:21.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Fujisawa-san, you came \Nto see Nyapollon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.64,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:28.11,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll bring that same \Npassion to this project, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:40.96,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,This month's Nanohana \NHall is really interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:42.20,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Mashiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:45.31,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to my advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:46.71,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:49.46,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:53.80,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,That was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.70,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-san, thanks for making the joyanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.03,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck on your exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:01.67,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I dedicate this brain \Nof mine to Suimei High!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:05.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I think Suimei would be in trouble \Nif it dropped to your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.36,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.76,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-san, this month's volume \Nwas super-interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:11.43,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:13.31,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You perfectly captured how boys and girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:15.24,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,get nervous as Valentine's Day approaches!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:18.16,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You can do anything if you put \Nyour mind to it, Mashiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting so condescending?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.16,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine's Day is the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's going through your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:27.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be worrying \Nabout tomorrow's exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:30.13,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:33.52,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, Valentine's Day \Nis a special day when girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.34,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,are allowed to display their courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.80,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-san, nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:42.30,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Misaki-san, \Nyou're on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.16,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She's making it by hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.79,Saku-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I hope she gets to give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.27,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.22,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko-chan, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:50.10,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:54.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, you left your laundry on\N the rack, so I folded them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.71,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't need to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:58.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be late \Ncoming home again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.11,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Should I heat up some rice for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The bath's ready, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:08.24,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'll eat first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:14.06,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,O-Onii-chan, what's your \Nrelationship with Nanami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:14.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:17.38,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing all these \Nthings for Nanami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.51,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right! \NSomething's definitely not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:21.56,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata does things for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:23.91,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you can't \Ndo them yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:30.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've always \Nwanted to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:34.10,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.57,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Always...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:58.72,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san's the one I should be \Nworried about, not Mashiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:01.68,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You both act like a couple that's \Nbeen living together for two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:04.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you pull such \Na realistic number from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.18,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:11.27,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mashiro-san, you're \Ndressed too immodestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.47,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Onii-chan! She'll attack you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.47,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you wearing any clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.69,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Because you weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:17.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You realize I'm setting out \Na futon for Yuko, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.59,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:21.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I can't warp \N or split myself in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a normal human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.74,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, how long are you \Ngoing to keep looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:26.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,At my embarrassing appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:30.97,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:32.92,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You dirty, nasty pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:34.29,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't come here dressed like \Nthat if you know how you look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:37.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do if I lose \Nmy cool in front of my sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:41.47,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you're a brute! A real brute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:49.34,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're you doing, Onii-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:50.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you talking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.43,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all shook up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just drying her hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,"Dry" not to stress!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:59.03,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.90,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're getting intimate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.42,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to make a fuss about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:05.30,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We always do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:08.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make it sound worse \Nthan it already is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:13.01,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,This is too mature for me! \NI'm worried about my test tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:15.62,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. You can do anything \Nyou put your mind to, Yuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:16.83,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,How condescending!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:21.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck on your exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:21.66,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:22.91,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Yuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:23.86,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:24.84,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.54,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, before I forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:29.07,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:30.19,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's a day early, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:30.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:35.53,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Mom helped me, but I made you \Nsome homemade chocolate this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:39.15,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to go straight home after \Nthe exam, so I'm giving it to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:42.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:45.22,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.28,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.99,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:52.69,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you really like, \NMashiro-san or Nanami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:56.46,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Dad wanted me to tell you to \Nstop being so indecisive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:58.44,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:01.23,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you're blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:02.34,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,So he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.55,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What did Yuko say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:04.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:05.47,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,How suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:06.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing suspicious about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:07.47,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:33.04,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,They say repeating "cacao mass"...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:34.80,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,over and over will make \Nyou feel like an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:40.98,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}#17 Valentine's Day is Chocolate Day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:37.70,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It seems eating too much chocolate \Ndoesn't actually make your nose bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:40.98,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Not being by Ryunosuke's side on \NValentine's Day is some awful "cacao mass."
